cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper involves the use of deep learning models (cs.LG) for predicting Alzheimer's disease progression based on MRI images (cs.CV), cognitive measures (cs.AI), and temporal dynamics (cs.NE) using recurrent neural networks. Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) for processing and analyzing neuropsychological data.
